                     <interp inst="t18220703-50-person492" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was brought back to the house - I sent for a constable.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Distress was the sole cause of my committing the deed.</p>
